[package]
name = "mdns-sd"
version = "0.10.4"
authors = [ "keepsimple <keepsimple@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.61.0"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/keepsimple1/mdns-sd"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/mdns-sd"
keywords = [ "mdns", "discovery", "service-discovery", "zeroconf", "dns-sd",]
categories = [ "network-programming",]
description = "mDNS Service Discovery library with no async runtime dependency"

[features]
async = [ "flume/async",]
logging = [ "log",]
default = [ "async", "logging",]

[dependencies]
polling = "2.1"

[dev-dependencies]
fastrand = "1.8"

[dependencies.flume]
version = "0.11"
default-features = false

[dependencies.if-addrs]
version = "0.10"
features = [ "link-local",]

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.socket2]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "all",]

[[bin]]
name = "core_bin"
path = "src/bin.rs"

[package]
name = "rqs_lib"
version = "0.11.5"
edition = "2024"
authors = [ "martichou",]

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0"
base64 = "0.22"
bytes = "1.10"
directories = "6.0"
futures = "0.3"
get_if_addrs = "0.5"
hex = "0.4"
hkdf = "0.12"
hmac = "0.12"
libaes = "0.7"
log = "0.4"
mime_guess = "2.0"
num-bigint = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.20"
prost = "0.13"
rand = "0.9"
sha2 = "0.10"
uuid = "1.15"

[build-dependencies]
prost-build = "0.13"

[features]
default = [ "experimental",]
experimental = [ "bluer", "btleplug",]

[dependencies.btleplug]
version = "0.11"
optional = true

[dependencies.mdns-sd]
git = "https://github.com/Martichou/mdns-sd"
branch = "unsolicited"

[dependencies.p256]
version = "0.13"
features = [ "ecdh",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.sys_metrics]
git = "https://github.com/Martichou/sys_metrics"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.43"
features = [ "macros", "rt", "rt-multi-thread", "net", "sync", "time", "io-util", "signal",]

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "rt",]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[profile.release]
lto = true
opt-level = 3
codegen-units = 1

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.bluer]
version = "0.17"
features = [ "full",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(target_arch = \"aarch64\", target_os = \"linux\"))".dependencies.dbus]
version = "0.9"
features = [ "vendored",]

[[bench]]
name = "cpu_bench"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "disks_bench"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "memory_bench"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "host_bench"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "network_bench"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "virt_bench"
harness = false

[package]
name = "sys_metrics"
version = "0.2.7"
authors = [ "Martichou <martichou.andre@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/sys_metrics"
repository = "https://github.com/Martichou/sys_metrics"
description = "Cross-platform library to gather stats/information from the host"
keywords = [ "metrics", "sysinfo", "psutil", "stats", "heim",]
license = "AGPL-3.0"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "os", "api-bindings",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1.4"
libc = "0.2"
glob = "0.3"

[dev-dependencies]
criterion = "0.4"

[lib]
bench = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[profile.release]
lto = true
opt-level = 3
codegen-units = 1

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
core-foundation-sys = "0.8"
io-kit-sys = "0.3"
mach = "0.3"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/martichou/mdns-sd"]
git = "https://github.com/martichou/mdns-sd"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "unsolicited"

[source."https://github.com/nozwock/rquickshare"]
git = "https://github.com/nozwock/rquickshare"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "17702edc9f8b0d1e67c50f125e03ca3f8c291f3c"

[source."https://github.com/martichou/sys_metrics"]
git = "https://github.com/martichou/sys_metrics"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
